65
00:04:39,150 --> 00:04:40,560
about the Censor case?

66
00:04:40,910 --> 00:04:42,230
Explain every detail.

67
00:04:44,710 --> 00:04:45,680
At this moment,

68
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:47,230
I will not

69
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:50,000
tell a single lie today.

70
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:51,120
At that time,

71
00:04:51,470 --> 00:04:53,390
Du Liang wasn't content
with being a County Constable.

72
00:04:53,710 --> 00:04:55,440
He wanted a transfer to the capital.

73
00:04:56,910 --> 00:04:58,080
To bribe officials,

74
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,640
he conspired
with Zheng Yuan, his advisor,

75
00:04:59,710 --> 00:05:00,520
and Qi Junshan

76
00:05:00,590 --> 00:05:02,350
to abduct women and imprison them
in an abandoned house.

77
00:05:02,790 --> 00:05:04,030
He also turned his own mansion

78
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,880
into a place of indulgence.

79
00:05:15,030 --> 00:05:15,710
Our dynasty has always had

80
00:05:15,790 --> 00:05:17,150
the tradition of recommending officials.

81
00:05:17,790 --> 00:05:19,120
It was originally to select
the virtuous and capable.

82
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:20,710
Yet,

83
00:05:20,790 --> 00:05:21,880
some exploit this system.

84
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:23,910
They went to Tongquan County

85
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,390
not just for women

86
00:05:26,030 --> 00:05:26,830
but also

87
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:27,710
for buying and selling

88
00:05:28,030 --> 00:05:28,790
official positions.

89
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,390
Guan Zhong the politician said,

90
00:05:31,910 --> 00:05:32,830
"Selling official positions

91
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:33,830
will lead to a nation's downfall
in ten years."

92
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:35,470
In the reign of Emperor Ling of Han,

93
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:37,270
those who traded ranks for wealth

94
00:05:37,350 --> 00:05:38,230
caused great disaster.

95
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:40,710
[Yang Wendao, Chief Censor]
And now, there are still people

96
00:05:40,790 --> 00:05:42,080
who dare to commit this crime.

97
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:45,680
If one can become an official
with mere silver,

98
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:48,790
where does this leave those
who study for a decade

99
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:51,520
and the imperial examinations
for talent selection?

100
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:52,910
Hai Yiping,

101
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,760
why did you go to Tongquan County?

102
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:56,960
What dealings

103
00:05:57,350 --> 00:05:58,320
did you have with Du Liang?

104
00:05:58,880 --> 00:05:59,960
I didn't go there

105
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:01,680
for women.

106
00:06:02,230 --> 00:06:03,680
I never laid a hand on them.

107
00:06:04,030 --> 00:06:05,230
I just made a mistake,

108
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,120
neither big nor small,

109
00:06:07,760 --> 00:06:09,030
in my early official career.

110
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:10,640
That mistake

111
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,270
is called "compromising to fit in."

112
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,120
Back then,

113
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:17,350
I was a Vice Director
of the Bureau of Honor,

114
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,710
responsible for assessing

115
00:06:18,790 --> 00:06:20,910
the performance and taxation records
of capital officials.

116
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,350
That is

117
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:24,000
how I became acquainted with Du Liang.

118
00:06:32,790 --> 00:06:34,080
Your records state

119
00:06:34,350 --> 00:06:36,230
that each man should pay
three dan of grain.

120
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:38,440
But I investigated among the people

121
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,830
and found
that they actually paid six dan.

122
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:42,640
That's double the recorded amount.

123
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:44,790
Where did the rest go?

124
00:06:46,710 --> 00:06:47,590
The salt granary

125
00:06:48,030 --> 00:06:49,760
is recorded to have 2,400 dan of salt

126
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,680
with 600 dan lost due to floods.

127
00:06:52,350 --> 00:06:53,710
I checked the granary.

128
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:56,960
There were no traces of flooding.

129
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,590
Your pockets...

130
00:07:01,230 --> 00:07:02,470
must be quite full.

131
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:03,830
Mr. Hai,

132
00:07:04,030 --> 00:07:06,270
you aren't aware of the situation
in Tongquan County.

133
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,440
The region is often plagued by bandits.

134
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:10,200
The court refuses to allocate funds.

135
00:07:10,350 --> 00:07:12,150
I had to handle the bandits myself,

136
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:14,080
which required additional expenses.

137
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,560
Check the prison records.

138
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:18,030
So many bandits
were arrested in a year.

139
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,080
I suppose you raise bandits

140
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:22,640
and arrest them yourself.

141
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,000
Du Liang,

142
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,830
do you have a death wish?

143
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:36,080
All right.

144
00:07:38,230 --> 00:07:40,270
If you want to convict me,

145
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:43,680
please stay the night.

146
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:45,350
Is that fine?

147
00:07:55,590 --> 00:07:56,470
Help!

148
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,120
Stop there!

149
00:08:01,350 --> 00:08:02,030
Get back.

150
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:02,880
Help.

151
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:04,270
Get in!

152
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:13,150
I suppose you recognized him.

153
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:16,000
Will you turn against
an old family friend...

154
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:18,910
and expose him?

155
00:08:34,800 --> 00:08:35,230
Yes.

156
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:36,280
Exactly.

157
00:08:39,540 --> 00:08:41,470
You're here too, Mr. Hai.

158
00:08:41,800 --> 00:08:43,960
I need someone to manage
the county's salt granary.

159
00:08:44,230 --> 00:08:44,830
I intend

160
