00:25:40,300 --> 00:25:40,910
You've

583
00:25:41,430 --> 00:25:42,390
made your mark

584
00:25:42,430 --> 00:25:43,340
on the capital.

585
00:25:44,060 --> 00:25:44,870
Everyone respects your courage

586
00:25:44,950 --> 00:25:46,060
in overturning the case
and eliminating the corrupt.

587
00:25:46,580 --> 00:25:47,670
Your Anxin House

588
00:25:47,870 --> 00:25:49,390
will soon be packed with people.

589
00:25:49,710 --> 00:25:52,340
There was once dead.

590
00:25:53,340 --> 00:25:54,990
People called me a witch.

591
00:25:55,710 --> 00:25:56,470
Now,

592
00:25:58,390 --> 00:25:59,670
they say I am brave.

593
00:26:02,340 --> 00:26:03,990
Does it matter

594
00:26:04,630 --> 00:26:06,150
whether it's a good or bad reputation

595
00:26:08,020 --> 00:26:08,990
or if it's true or false?

596
00:26:11,260 --> 00:26:11,710
By the way,

597
00:26:12,430 --> 00:26:13,540
Hai Yiping's family...

598
00:26:14,190 --> 00:26:14,670
Don't worry.

599
00:26:15,710 --> 00:26:16,740
Her Majesty has not directed any anger

600
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:17,470
toward them.

601
00:26:17,870 --> 00:26:18,820
I heard that Madam Hai

602
00:26:19,100 --> 00:26:20,670
is taking Hai Yan to leave the capital.

603
00:26:23,670 --> 00:26:24,740
What should we do?

604
00:26:24,780 --> 00:26:25,260
Yeah.

605
00:26:25,260 --> 00:26:25,910
We should go back to our hometown.

606
00:26:25,910 --> 00:26:26,740
What do we do?

607
00:26:27,340 --> 00:26:28,470
All right. Take care.

608
00:26:28,670 --> 00:26:29,020
All right.

609
00:26:29,470 --> 00:26:29,910
Let's go.

610
00:26:30,340 --> 00:26:30,910
Take care.

611
00:26:42,800 --> 00:26:46,700
[Hai Mansion]

612
00:28:07,390 --> 00:28:07,990
Ping'an.

613
00:28:53,260 --> 00:28:54,230
This is a rouge

614
00:28:54,230 --> 00:28:55,190
I just bought in Yangzhou.

615
00:28:55,540 --> 00:28:56,430
I haven't tried it yet.

616
00:28:57,260 --> 00:28:57,710
Come on.

617
00:28:58,150 --> 00:28:58,870
Put it on me.

618
00:29:01,340 --> 00:29:02,150
Me?

619
00:29:04,710 --> 00:29:06,260
I'm not very good at this.

620
00:29:14,500 --> 00:29:15,060
Ping'an,

621
00:29:16,190 --> 00:29:17,190
upon hearing of the overturning

622
00:29:17,190 --> 00:29:18,580
of the Censor case in Yangzhou,

623
00:29:18,990 --> 00:29:20,150
I rushed back at once.

624
00:29:20,740 --> 00:29:21,710
I inquired along the way

625
00:29:22,060 --> 00:29:23,500
and learned of all that had happened

626
00:29:23,580 --> 00:29:24,630
since I left the capital.

627
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:27,230
It's all my fault.

628
00:29:28,430 --> 00:29:29,580
I should never have left.

629
00:29:30,260 --> 00:29:31,340
If I had stayed,

630
00:29:31,820 --> 00:29:32,780
perhaps you and Danxin...

631
00:29:32,910 --> 00:29:33,820
There is no "perhaps."

632
00:29:36,260 --> 00:29:37,190
This matter

633
00:29:38,340 --> 00:29:39,340
has nothing to do with you.

634
00:29:42,870 --> 00:29:44,390
Fortunately, with the case overturned,

635
00:29:44,870 --> 00:29:46,340
Danxin's name has been cleared.

636
00:29:46,710 --> 00:29:47,780
Everyone now knows

637
00:29:48,150 --> 00:29:49,230
that Danxin took that step

638
00:29:49,300 --> 00:29:50,630
to expose

639
00:29:50,990 --> 00:29:52,150
Hai Yiping's true nature.

640
00:29:55,340 --> 00:29:55,910
Ping'an,

641
00:29:57,430 --> 00:29:58,950
now that it's all over,

642
00:30:00,020 --> 00:30:00,990
what is your plan?

643
00:30:03,470 --> 00:30:04,470
I don't know why,

644
00:30:06,190 --> 00:30:07,060
but these days,

645
00:30:07,910 --> 00:30:09,300
I keep thinking of the past.

646
00:30:10,470 --> 00:30:11,950
After the Censor case,

647
00:30:12,540 --> 00:30:14,430
I despised everything about myself,

648
00:30:14,670 --> 00:30:16,430
living in a daze.

649
00:30:16,740 --> 00:30:18,470
Then, I met Ruan Qin.

650
00:30:18,910 --> 00:30:21,150
Watching her,
tormented by mental anguish,

651
00:30:21,500 --> 00:30:23,630
jump off the cliff before me.

652
00:30:24,470 --> 00:30:25,500
It made me realize

653
00:30:25,910 --> 00:30:27,150
that the pain of the heart

654
00:30:27,190 --> 00:30:28,540
is no less than the pain of the body.

655
00:30:29,580 --> 00:30:30,390
From then on,

656
00:30:30,710 --> 00:30:32,910
I resolved to use my talents

657
00:30:33,300 --> 00:30:35,780
to study the art of healing the mind.

658
00:30:36,580 --> 00:30:38,260
Though I have healed many,

659
00:30:38,670 --> 00:30:40,470
I have never been able
to forgive myself.

660
00:30:40,870 --> 00:30:42,910
It was only upon meeting
Danxin and Cailian

661
00:30:43,260 --> 00:30:44,990
that I found a chance at redemption.

662
00:30:46,060 --> 00:30:47,060
From that moment,

663
00:30:48,540 --> 00:30:49,990
I swore to devote my life

664
00:30:50,470 --> 00:30:51,870
to the Censor case.

665
00:30:53,060 --> 00:30:54,990
Until justice was served,

666
00:30:55,580 --> 00:30:57,100
I would never stop.

667
00:30:58,820 --> 00:30:59,580
Now,

668
00:31:01,780 --> 00:31:03,710
the case has ended suddenly.

669
00:31:06,230 --> 00:31:07,870
But Cailian and Danxin...

670
00:31:10,190 --> 00:31:11,230
are gone.

671
00:31:20,630 --> 00:31:21,230
Ping'an,

672
00:31:21,580 --> 00:31:22,540
without you,

673
00:31:22,950 --> 00:31:24,300
no one knows how many more years
it would have taken

674
00:31:24,340 --> 00:31:25,300
to clear this injustice.

675
00:31:26,060 --> 00:31:27,340
You, too, were a victim.

676
00:31:27,870 --> 00:31:29,230
No one will blame you anymore.

677
00:31:33,990 --> 00:31:34,670
What about you?

678
00:31:35,710 --> 00:31:37,470
Will you stay at Wanguoxiang Tavern?

679
00:31:38,190 --> 00:31:39,260
I haven't decided yet.

680
00:31:40,230 --> 00:31:41,260
You've lost more weight

681
00:31:41,710 --> 00:31:42,710
since I last saw you.

682
00:31:43,340 --> 00:31:45,020
Stop worrying about treating others.

683
00:31:46,190 --> 00:31:47,390
Take care of yourself first.

684
00:32:00,910 --> 00:32:03,230
I plead guilty before Your Majesty.

685
00:32:03,710 --> 00:32:05,990
You played a key role
in overturning the Censor case.

686
00:32:06,230 --> 00:32:07,190
Why plead guilty?

687
00:32:08,060 --> 00:32:09,340
I disobeyed Your Majesty's order

688
00:32:09,910 --> 00:32:11,500
and took it upon myself
to investigate the case.

689
00:32:12,100 --> 00:32:13,500
After discovering the gate incident,

690
00:32:13,740 --> 00:32:14,950
I failed to report it in time.

691
00:32:15,630 --> 00:32:15,990
Therefore,

692
00:32:16,630 --> 00:32:17,390
I plead guilty.

693
00:32:25,500 --> 00:32:26,500
Was it

694
00:32:27,390 --> 00:32:29,190
that you failed to report it in time

695
00:32:29,540 --> 00:32:31,100
or that you deliberately withheld it?

696
00:32:31,670 --> 00:32:32,630
First Li Zongxu,

697
00:32:32,740 --> 00:32:33,910
then Hai Yiping.

698
00:32:34,260 --> 00:32:35,390
You acted on your own accord,

699
00:32:35,470 --> 00:32:36,580
defying my will.

700
00:32:36,910 --> 00:32:37,390
I

701
00:32:38,190 --> 00:32:39,870
have tolerated you again and again,

702
00:32:40,670 --> 00:32:42,990
yet you keep pushing the limits.

703
00:32:43,100 --> 00:32:44,060
Your Majesty is a wise ruler

704
00:32:44,500 --> 00:32:45,540
who always speaks of
prioritizing the greater good.

705
00:32:45,910 --> 00:32:46,470
I believe

706
00:32:46,670 --> 00:32:48,100
that both the salt case
and the Censor case

707
00:32:48,390 --> 00:32:49,390
concern the people

708
00:32:49,670 --> 00:32:50,500
and thus the greater good.

709
00:32:51,020 --> 00:32:51,820
Tell me,

710
00:32:52,820 --> 00:32:54,020
do you still regard me

711
00:32:54,540 --> 00:32:56,060
as your sovereign?

712
00:32:58,500 --> 00:32:59,780
The people are Your Majesty's.

713
00:33:00,020 --> 00:33:02,020
You love them, and so must I.

714
00:33:02,340 --> 00:33:02,910
I believe

715
00:33:03,230 --> 00:33:03,820
that loyalty to the people

716
00:33:04,100 --> 00:33:04,950
is loyalty to the ruler.

717
00:33:07,230 --> 00:33:09,540
How eloquent.

718
00:33:10,950 --> 00:33:12,870
Hai Yiping often spoke before me

719
00:33:13,230 --> 00:33:15,190
of how, in ancient governance,
love for the people was paramount

720
00:33:15,340 --> 00:33:16,820
and the people came before the realm.

721
00:33:17,150 --> 00:33:19,020
You were in contact often lately.

722
00:33:19,260 --> 00:33:21,100
You even speak alike.

723
00:33:22,740 --> 00:33:23,300
Your Majesty.

724
00:33:24,500 --> 00:33:26,740
You need not concern yourself
with the salt matter any longer.

725
00:33:26,990 --> 00:33:27,630
From now on,

726
00:33:28,390 --> 00:33:29,390
unless summoned,

727
00:33:30,060 --> 00:33:31,430
you need not report to me.

728
00:33:31,910 --> 00:33:32,740
Simply focus

729
00:33:33,020 --> 00:33:34,950
on your duties
at the Court of Judicial Review.

730
00:33:35,470 --> 00:33:36,020
As you command,

731
00:33:36,820 --> 00:33:38,340
Your Majesty.

732
00:33:41,710 --> 00:33:42,190
Mr. Yuan,

733
00:33:43,060 --> 00:33:43,870
after the Censor case,

734
00:33:44,190 --> 00:33:45,470
did Her Majesty mention
any reward for you?

735
00:33:45,710 --> 00:33:46,150
No.

736
00:33:47,990 --> 00:33:49,390
The evaluation by the Department
of Merit Assessments is finished.

737
00:33:49,870 --> 00:33:50,990
Many from humble backgrounds
were promoted.

738
00:33:51,710 --> 00:33:53,100
You solved a great case
and rendered great service,

739
00:33:53,300 --> 00:33:54,340
yet not a single reward for you.

740
00:33:54,670 --> 00:33:55,780
Her Majesty is truly biased.

741
00:33:57,390 --> 00:33:58,100
The capital

742
00:33:58,340 --> 00:33:59,230
is a square grid,

743
00:33:59,990 --> 00:34:00,990
much like a chessboard.

744
00:34:02,340 --> 00:34:03,150
But I refuse to be

745
00:34:03,230 --> 00:34:04,430
anyone's pawn.

746
00:34:06,540 --> 00:34:07,300
Go ahead.

747
00:34:07,500 --> 00:34:08,350
I have other matters to attend to.

748
00:34:08,870 --> 00:34:09,270
Yes.

749
00:34:12,620 --> 00:34:19,750
[Kangping Mansion]

750
00:34:22,750 --> 00:34:23,310
Your Highness.

751
00:34:24,060 --> 00:34:24,700
Minister Yuan,

752
00:34:24,870 --> 00:34:25,580
what brings you here?

753
00:34:25,620 --> 00:34:27,910
Regarding the Mang Gutter people's
tower construction task,

754
00:34:28,180 --> 00:34:28,870
I have yet to thank

755
00:34:28,910 --> 00:34:30,020
Your Highness.

756
00:34:30,310 --> 00:34:31,100
I have come today

757
00:34:31,620 --> 00:34:32,830
to express my gratitude

758
00:34:32,910 --> 00:34:33,700
for Your Highness's assistance.

759
00:34:33,830 --> 00:34:35,950
The Directorate for the Palace Buildings
is responsible for it.

760
00:34:36,100 --> 00:34:37,220
It should not burden the people.

761
00:34:37,830 --> 00:34:38,540
No need for thanks.

762
00:34:39,310 --> 00:34:41,470
Last time, Kang brought
rock sugar cakes home.

763
00:34:42,350 --> 00:34:43,100
Thank you.

764
00:34:43,430 --> 00:34:45,020
It was nothing.

765
00:34:45,390 --> 00:34:46,540
If Your Highness enjoys them,

766
00:34:46,980 --> 00:34:47,430
it is

767
00:34:47,980 --> 00:34:48,910
my honor.

768
00:34:49,340 --> 00:34:50,060
Good timing.

769
00:34:51,020 --> 00:34:52,180
Come with me
to Chancellor Mei's mansion.

770
00:34:55,420 --> 00:34:56,500
[Mei Mansion]

771
00:34:56,500 --> 00:34:57,700
Hai Yiping

772
00:34:58,220 --> 00:34:59,140
took the wrong path.

773
00:34:59,820 --> 00:35:00,790
His death was predestined.

774
00:35:01,340 --> 00:35:02,140
Mr. Mei,

775
00:35:02,580 --> 00:35:03,830
please do not grieve too much.

776
00:35:06,700 --> 00:35:07,580
After all,

777
00:35:07,940 --> 00:35:09,220
he was still my disciple.

778
00:35:09,540 --> 00:35:10,140
He

779
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:12,430
understood caution and change

780
00:35:13,460 --> 00:35:15,140
yet never learned the art of retreat.

781
00:35:16,500 --> 00:35:17,470
Few people

782
00:35:17,860 --> 00:35:19,310
can truly accept retreat.

783
00:35:20,300 --> 00:35:21,270
During the trial,

784
00:35:21,860 --> 00:35:23,060
I was unable to do anything

785
00:35:23,100 --> 00:35:23,790
for you.

786
00:35:24,540 --> 00:35:25,700
I apologize.

787
00:35:26,020 --> 00:35:27,500
You handled the case with impartiality.

788
00:35:27,660 --> 00:35:28,470
Why the apology?

789
00:35:34,060 --> 00:35:35,620
What do you think of Ye Ping'an?

790
00:35:37,460 --> 00:35:39,060
She is unpredictable.

791
00:35:39,860 --> 00:35:40,500
Fortunately,

792
00:35:41,060 --> 00:35:42,790
Her Majesty dismissed her

793
00:35:43,140 --> 00:35:44,020
before granting her any real power.

794
00:35:45,820 --> 00:35:46,350
You see,

795
00:35:47,220 --> 00:35:48,180
Zhuangzi once said,

796
00:35:48,660 --> 00:35:49,870
"When virtue is abandoned,

797
00:35:50,140 --> 00:35:51,180
the path is cleared."

798
00:35:52,340 --> 00:35:53,620
Ye Ping'an achieved it.

799
00:35:54,060 --> 00:35:56,430
She discarded false reputation

800
00:35:56,500 --> 00:35:57,750
and orchestrated plans,

801
00:35:58,220 --> 00:35:59,310
understanding human nature.

802
00:36:00,500 --> 00:36:01,390
She's a rare talent.

803
00:36:03,780 --> 00:36:04,790
It's a pity

804
00:36:04,980 --> 00:36:06,700
that Her Majesty won't employ her.

805
00:36:08,020 --> 00:36:09,500
What a waste of talent.

806
00:36:10,100 --> 00:36:12,100
If Her Majesty
truly did not wish to keep her,

807
00:36:12,220 --> 00:36:13,910
she would have banished her
from the capital long ago.

808
00:36:14,820 --> 00:36:15,580
Look

809
00:36:15,940 --> 00:36:17,060
at this silk figurine I painted

810
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:18,620
and his furrowed brows
and drooping eyes.

811
00:36:18,660 --> 00:36:20,220
Looks like Vice Minister Li.

812
00:36:22,020 --> 00:36:23,430
Speaking of whom,

813
00:36:25,220 --> 00:36:26,870
he's remained silent

814
00:36:27,300 --> 00:36:28,540
since Her Majesty's new policies
were announced.

815
00:36:29,060 --> 00:36:30,220
That is unlike him.

816
00:36:31,500 --> 00:36:32,540
Had these policies

817
00:36:32,580 --> 00:36:33,790
been issued earlier,

818
00:36:34,020 --> 00:36:35,620
the noble families

819
00:36:35,700 --> 00:36:37,580
would have fiercely opposed them.

820
00:36:37,980 --> 00:36:39,580
Her Majesty has timed it well.

821
00:36:40,100 --> 00:36:42,270
First, Her Majesty
reopened the Censor case,

822
00:36:42,900 --> 00:36:44,270
striking fear into them,

823
00:36:44,700 --> 00:36:46,580
before announcing the reforms,

824
00:36:46,860 --> 00:36:48,060
leaving no room for opposition.

825
00:36:50,020 --> 00:36:51,270
The Li family

826
00:36:51,500 --> 00:36:53,660
is now focused on self-preservation.

827
00:36:54,300 --> 00:36:55,660
They will remain quiet for a while.

828
00:37:00,340 --> 00:37:01,180
Shaocheng

829
00:37:01,380 --> 00:37:02,990
rendered great merit in the Censor case.

830
00:37:03,540 --> 00:37:04,430
Yet in the recent evaluations,

831
00:37:04,500 --> 00:37:05,870
he was given no promotion.

832
00:37:06,900 --> 00:37:07,470
Mr. Mei.

833
00:37:09,020 --> 00:37:11,580
Shall we jointly recommend Shaocheng

834
00:37:12,020 --> 00:37:13,540
for the Right Aide
of the Department of State Affairs?

835
00:37:13,660 --> 00:37:14,180
How does that sound?

836
00:37:19,380 --> 00:37:20,580
My experience is still shallow.

837
00:37:21,220 --> 00:37:22,500
I dare not deserve such recognition

838
00:37:22,860 --> 00:37:23,540
from Your Highness

839
00:37:23,820 --> 00:37:24,790
and Mr. Mei.

840
00:37:25,180 --> 00:37:25,870
Why do you say that?

841
00:37:26,380 --> 00:37:27,100
Wang Chongdao,

842
00:37:27,300 --> 00:37:29,100
with no merit or virtue,

843
00:37:29,340 --> 00:37:31,060
was appointed
as Vice Chamberlain for Ceremonials.

844
00:37:31,140 --> 00:37:31,990
Why can't you?

845
00:37:32,540 --> 00:37:33,470
Her Majesty has decreed

846
00:37:33,700 --> 00:37:35,270
that appointments
shall not be based on birth.

847
00:37:36,060 --> 00:37:38,310
Who would dare defy Her Majesty?

848
00:37:39,020 --> 00:37:40,750
His Highness makes a valid point.

849
00:37:41,500 --> 00:37:43,830
Shaocheng's background
is far from ordinary.

850
00:37:44,060 --> 00:37:44,580
Then...

851
00:37:45,460 --> 00:37:47,500
But the Right Aide position

852
00:37:47,540 --> 00:37:48,750
is now a coveted position.

853
00:37:49,060 --> 00:37:50,870
Recommending Shaocheng at this moment

854
00:37:51,060 --> 00:37:52,470
may invite opposition.

855
00:37:53,020 --> 00:37:54,350
What would be your opinion?

856
00:37:59,500 --> 00:38:00,470
Give it to Xu Ling.

857
00:38:07,500 --> 00:38:08,430
That's brilliant.

858
00:38:10,980 --> 00:38:13,700
Xu Ling is the grandson
of the Chancellor of the past dynasty.

859
00:38:13,940 --> 00:38:14,950
He has an excellent lineage

860
00:38:15,020 --> 00:38:16,390
but is arrogant,

861
00:38:16,780 --> 00:38:17,990
impatient,

862
00:38:18,380 --> 00:38:19,620
and prone to mistakes.

863
00:38:21,300 --> 00:38:22,270
Do you understand now, Shaocheng?

864
00:38:22,860 --> 00:38:24,350
You'll have to endure another year.

865
00:38:25,500 --> 00:38:26,990
I never dared to hope for such an honor.

866
00:38:27,500 --> 00:38:28,830
There is no endurance to speak of.

867
00:38:29,380 --> 00:38:30,750
You're thirty-four now, are you not?

868
00:38:32,420 --> 00:38:34,430
Xian'er's temperament aligns with yours,

